text: Édouard Schmoll (born 9 December 1889) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1889 births Category:Year of death missing Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:People from Roncq
